 <p style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: 16px; color: #333;">
  Hide was born in Arizona — where sun, heat, and dry air test your skin every day. But this isn’t just skincare for the desert. It’s skincare for anyone who’s tired of products that don’t work, don’t last, or don’t feel real. Everything we make is built to nourish and protect, no matter the climate.
</p>

